==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nodical
<hw>Nod"ic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
the nodes; from a node to the same node again; <as>as, the
<ex>nodical</ex> revolutions of the moon</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Nodical month</b></col>. <cd>See <cref>Lunar
month</cref>, under <er>Month</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nodosarine</ent>⟦br⟧
